  "content": "<p>No matter what state you live in, you can enroll in affordable, quality health coverage.</p><h3>State Medicaid expansion</h3><p>Some states expanded their Medicaid programs to cover more people. <a href=\"/lower-costs\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"4bcf3697-3fc1-4cb2-9de4-8735fbf13eae\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"38081\" data-entity-bundle=\"explainer\" title=\"Saving money on health insurance\">Check if you might qualify for lower costs.</a></p><h3>How to apply for health coverage</h3><p>How you apply depends on if your state has its own Marketplace. Pick your state to find how to get coverage.</p><div data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"3db895b6-0644-4443-9460-4a0db8c02736\" data-embed-button=\"embedded_app\" data-entity-embed-display=\"view_mode:node.embedded_app\" data-langcode=\"en\" data-entity-embed-display-settings=\"[]\" class=\"embedded-entity\">\n<article class=\"node node--type-embedded-app node--view-mode-embedded-app\">\n\n  \n    \n\n  \n  <div class=\"node__content\">\n      \n            <div class=\"field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden field__item\"><h2><a href=\"/node/39426\" hreflang=\"en\">State Dropdown - Get Coverage</a></h2></div>\n      \n  <div class=\"field field--name-field-embedded-app-id field--type-string field--label-inline clearfix\">\n    <div class=\"field__label\">English App ID:</div>\n              <div class=\"field__item\">state-dropdown-get-coverage</div>\n          </div>\n\n  <div class=\"field field--name-field-spanish-app-id field--type-string field--label-inline clearfix\">\n    <div class=\"field__label\">Spanish App ID:</div>\n              <div class=\"field__item\">state-dropdown-get-coverage</div>\n          </div>\n\n  <div class=\"field field--name-field-application-type field--type-entity-reference field--label-inline clearfix\">\n    <div class=\"field__label\">Application Type:</div>\n              <div class=\"fiel